a:r.a:t: Emerging Trends Detection Model gets applied to a sampling of top queries on a schedule
Model identifies conceptual clusters of potential interest
Application identifies clusters that already exist as topics and net new clusters and their L1 affiliation
The user receives and reviews new cluster suggestions (declining, merging into existing topics, creating new topics)
Identifying new emerging concepts, suggesting them for review / inclusion; monitoring existing topics’ health
